    },
    {
      "id": "b1c9689a_f579f9e8",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/a1policymanagement/resources/envsubst/daemon.sh",
      "patchset_number": 10,
      "line": 27,
      "message": "Well, I can do it this way, but it appeared to me a bit more problematic, because I'm not able to turn executable bit on mounted config map either as runtime operation (read-only filesystem) or via volume's defaultMode parameter (https://v1-18.docs.kubernetes.io/docs/reference/generated/kubernetes-api/v1.18/#configmapvolumesource-v1-core - executable flag wasn't applied in my case) so it would required some more magic actions...\nWhat do you think?",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5550,
        "name": "Konrad Banka",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "kbanka.os@gmail.com",
        "username": "kbanka"
      },
      "updated": "2020-11-05 14:16:34.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "1ac8f729_ab289108",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "7053f5d9_ae372a20",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/a1policymanagement/resources/envsubst/daemon.sh",
      "patchset_number": 10,
      "line": 27,
      "message": "Anyway, I've updated review (#11) with change using configmap. I'm wondering if it will work fine in Gating CI. Tested localy, defaultMode even though it was set to \"0555\"[int] was corrected to \"0644\"[int] in runtime, but after manual edit later again to \"0555\"[int] this setting was preserved...\nLet's see then, I'll vote -1 for now not to have it merged because it appear not to work fully, but I hope for your input in this case",
      "author": {
        "account_id": 5550,
        "name": "Konrad Banka",
        "display_name": null,
        "email": "kbanka.os@gmail.com",
        "username": "kbanka"
      },
      "updated": "2020-11-05 14:40:51.000000000",
      "in_reply_to": "b1c9689a_f579f9e8",
      "unresolved": true
    },
    {
      "id": "eca21680_7a45f240",
      "file_path": "kubernetes/a1policymanagement/resources/envsubst/daemon.sh",
      "patchset_number": 10,
      "line": 27,
      "message": "Well, looks like in Gating CI results are same as in my local env: DefaultMode is changed to 0644[oct] (420[dec]), so didn't preserve execute permissions - https://logs.onap.org/onap-integration/gating//114366-11/infrastructure-healthcheck/k8s/kubernetes-status/pod-onap-a1policymanagement-7857fb9f97-xk2g4.html . @Krzysztof - do you have any advice?",
      "author": {
